Samantha Caine, suburban homemaker, is the ideal mom to her 8 year old daughter
Caitlin. She lives in Honesdale, PA, has a job teaching school and makes the
best Rice Krispie treats in town. But when she receives a bump on her head, she
begins to remember small parts of her previous life as a lethal, top-secret
agent.

272p = 272 lines of pixels in a 16:9 aspect ratio video with a 480 pixel width.

A 480x208 pixel video with an aspect ratio of 2.35:1 or a 480x352 pixel video
with an aspect ratio of 4:3 are also considered 272p.

272p m4v/mp4 format videos are easily played on PCs, Macs, smartphones, tablets,
and portable multimedia players such as iPods, Zunes, PSPs, etc.
